You are working on Ally, a personal AI companion app.

## Stack
- Bun runtime (NOT Node.js) — use `bun` for all commands
- Turborepo monorepo with Bun workspaces
- Elysia backend (apps/api/) — Bun-native, TypeScript only
- Expo 55 / React Native (apps/mobile/) — NativeWind, Zustand, expo-router
- Neon PostgreSQL via Drizzle ORM — relational source of truth (no pgvector; embeddings are in Qdrant)
- Qdrant Cloud — vector store for memory_facts and memory_episodes
- FalkorDB Cloud — entity graph (Cypher) + BullMQ queue backend (Redis protocol)
- Claude Haiku 4.5 (fast) + Sonnet 4.6 (quality) via @anthropic-ai/sdk — with server-side web search and custom tools
- Voyage AI voyage-4-lite for contextual embeddings (1024 dims)
- Better Auth (cookie-based sessions)

## Code Style
- TypeScript strict mode everywhere
- ESM only (import/export, never require)
- No `any` unless interfacing with untyped libraries — prefer `unknown` + narrowing
- No comments that narrate what code does — only explain non-obvious intent
- camelCase for variables/functions, PascalCase for types/classes
- Thin route handlers — business logic in services/ or ai/
- Shared types go in packages/shared, not duplicated

## Architecture
- Memory system has 6 tiers: hot (JSONB profile with dynamicAttributes), warm (session summaries), upcoming events, semantic facts (Postgres + Qdrant), episodic (Postgres + Qdrant, TTL), entity graph (FalkorDB)
- Memory extraction is real-time via BullMQ queue (FalkorDB Redis backend), not cron
- Session windowing: conversations split into sessions (30min gap), each summarized by Claude
- Hybrid retrieval: 3-stage (Qdrant dense + Qdrant keyword + FalkorDB entity graph), merged via RRF
- Weekly consolidation promotes episodes → semantic facts → dynamicAttributes in hot profile
- AI has tools: web search, remember_fact, recall_memory, set_reminder (apps/api/src/ai/tools.ts)
- Model routing: Haiku for casual, Sonnet for complex/emotional messages
- AI prompts are centralized in apps/api/src/ai/prompts.ts
- All AI calls go through apps/api/src/ai/client.ts (with tool-use agentic loops)
- Tiers: free_trial (14 days, full Basic features) → basic → premium. No permanent free tier.
- Database schema is in apps/api/src/db/schema.ts + apps/api/src/db/auth-schema.ts (Drizzle)
- Never modify _legacy/ — it's reference only

## Do NOT
- Use npm/yarn/npx (use bun/bunx)
- Add Python code
- Add Express.js patterns
- Use CommonJS (require/module.exports)
- Hardcode secrets
- Skip type checking (always run tsc --noEmit)
